primary_asset_contracts.name: DeepBlack
primary_asset_contracts.description:
Minted in 2019, DeepBlack is the first end-to-end AI artist on the Ethereum blockchain. 

The DeepBlack collection is limited to 3,073 fine art pieces. No more will ever be minted or created.

The DeepBlack community consists of historical NFT collectors and NFT connoisseurs alike. They affectionately call themselves the GANGang.
